---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';

import { visualNovels } from '@constants/blog';

const meta = {
  title: 'Blog | CoNexus',
  nav: 'Blog',
  arrow: '/learn/blog',
  header: 'Best Visual Novels',
  subheading:
    'Looking for the best visual novels to play in 2025? Explore immersive, choice-driven stories across romance, mystery, fantasy, and more — available online and on all platforms.',
};
---

<Layout {...meta}>
  <header class="blog-title">
    <img
      class="shad-behind"
      src="/learn/blog/best-visual-novels.avif"
      alt="Visual novels"
    />
    <h3>Best Visual Novels to Play in 2025</h3>
  </header>

  <article class="blog-page">
    <p>
      Visual novels blend storytelling, art, music, and interactivity into one
      immersive experience. With roots in both traditional fiction and gaming,
      they let players explore complex narratives while making choices that
      influence character relationships, plot developments, and endings.
    </p>
    <p>
      Whether you’re new to the genre or a longtime fan, 2025 offers a growing
      library of visual novels that cover every theme — from romance and horror
      to science fiction and psychological drama.
    </p>
    <hr />
    <h5>
      Here’s a curated list of some of the best visual novels to play right now:
    </h5>
    <ol class="cards-list">
      {
        visualNovels.map(
          ({ name, bestFor, platform, pricing, description, url }) => {
            return (
              <a
                class={name === 'CoNexus' ? 'card green-card' : 'card'}
                href={url}
              >
                <h4>{name}</h4>
                <span class="details">
                  <p>
                    Best for: <strong>{bestFor}</strong>
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    Platform: <strong>{platform}</strong>
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    Pricing: <strong>{pricing}</strong>
                  </p>
                </span>
                <p>{description}</p>
              </a>
            );
          }
        )
      }
    </ol>
    <hr />
    <h5>Final Thoughts</h5>
    <p>
      The visual novel space continues to evolve with hybrid formats, player
      customization, and stronger tools for creators. Whether you’re seeking a
      complex sci-fi narrative or a personal romance you can shape, there’s
      something out there for you.
    </p>
    <p>
      And with platforms like CoNexus expanding what a visual novel can be —
      adding AI, personalization, and live remixing — the future of this genre
      is more dynamic, accessible, and creative than ever.
    </p>
    <p>Start reading, start playing, and see where your choices take you.</p>
  </article>
</Layout>
